ason why you want to go to Chiba university.  While  I realize I am treading on dangerous ground by saying this, in general, most Japanese universities are not as highly regarded as their western counterparts (mostly because most Japanese universities are a joke...).  If you really want to learn something, and it's not something that Chiba university is particularly famous for, you might be better off studying in the states and then doing a study abroad in Japan...?  <br>
<br>
